{"id":260329,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/10/叙利亚的正义风暴和中国的天降祥瑞/","date":"2012-10-31T10:45:43Z","modified":"2018-10-05T03:42:23Z","title":"叙利亚的正义风暴和中国的天降祥瑞","content":"<p>无论是大自然造成的灾难还是天空中云朵的变化，对某些人来说都是富有意义的。飓风“桑迪”重创了美国东海岸，造成约300亿美元的损失，夺走了100多条人命。拥护叙利亚总统阿萨德的Syrian Army News声称，飓风是叙利亚和伊朗运用先进技术改变气候创造的反西方气候武器，以惩罚西方对阿萨德叙利亚的恐吓。与此同时，中国官方媒体微博帐号新华视点发表照片说“今早8时许，京城东南方上空突现奇观：太阳恰从一片云彩后面照射下来，祥云形状酷似大鹏展翅”，新华视点称之为“祥云展翅”，而中国气象网称这是“十八大来临前的祥兆”，该微博已被删除(截图)。<img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://solidot.org.feedsportal.com/c/33236/f/556826/s/2511f9e9/mf.gif\" border=\"0\" /></p>\n<div>\n<table border=\"0\">\n<tr>\n<td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/viral/sendEmail.cfm?lang=en&#038;title=%E5%8F%99%E5%88%A9%E4%BA%9A%E7%9A%84%E6%AD%A3%E4%B9%89%E9%A3%8E%E6%9A%B4%E5%92%8C%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E7%9A%84%E5%A4%A9%E9%99%8D%E7%A5%A5%E7%91%9E&#038;link=http%3A%2F%2Finternet.solidot.org%2Farticle.pl%3Fsid%3D12%2F10%2F31%2F0835233%26amp%3Bfrom%3Drss\"><img src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/images/emailthis2.gif\" border=\"0\" /></a></td>\n<td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://res.feedsportal.com/viral/bookmark.cfm?title=%E5%8F%99%E5%88%A9%E4%BA%9A%E7%9A%84%E6%AD%A3%E4%B9%89%E9%A3%8E%E6%9A%B4%E5%92%8C%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E7%9A%84%E5%A4%A9%E9%99%8D%E7%A5%A5%E7%91%9E&#038;link=http%3A%2F%2Finternet.solidot.org%2Farticle.pl%3Fsid%3D12%2F10%2F31%2F0835233%26amp%3Bfrom%3Drss\"><img src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/images/bookmark.gif\" border=\"0\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n</div>\n<p><a href=\"http://da.feedsportal.com/r/148658359583/u/49/f/556826/c/33236/s/2511f9e9/a2.htm\"><img src=\"http://da.feedsportal.com/r/148658359583/u/49/f/556826/c/33236/s/2511f9e9/a2.img\" border=\"0\" /></a><img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://pi.feedsportal.com/r/148658359583/u/49/f/556826/c/33236/s/2511f9e9/a2t.img\" border=\"0\" /></p>\n<div>\n<a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?a=_DZQ8VP1iIE:EnpAECrFF-Q:yIl2AUoC8zA\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.co